---
By: Isaac of Syria
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 220
    Verse: 10
Tags:
  - Habits
---
Once a habit demands something and its request is not fulfilled, the next
time you will find it weaker. But once you fulfill its will, the next time
you will find it fall on you with much greater force.
